creator: Funds Grip
descriptionHtml: Funds Grip is an app for financial investors to view there investment portfolio, wealth reports, calculators, goal tracker and many more such features. Funds Grip is conceived and developed by Redvision as an extension to there award winning financial advisor portfolio management system. To access Funds Grip app you will have to be registered user with your financial advisor.

What's New-
From today, you'll notice the improved UI and Font Size that will be bold and visible. Also, there is a new Robo feature in the application.
